		"description": "We're working on model-view binding on controls like tableviews that rely on a collection, but it would be good to also allow single components to bind to a single model. In this way, changes to the state of a model can make changes to singular components like Labels, TextFields, Buttons, etc...\r\n\r\nraw protoype\r\n{code:lang=xml}\r\n<Model src=\"myModel\"/>\r\n\r\n<Label text=\"{myModel.text}\"/>\r\n<TextField value=\"{myModel.someValue}\"/>\r\n{code}",
